<item>
            <title>[LU-19761] Build Lustre against zfs-2.4.0</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19761</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre does not build against zfs-2.4.0.&#160; It needs to update it&apos;s dmu_&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;write|hold&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; calls to pass in an extra flags parameter.&#160; It also needs to `#define _KERNEL 1` when it&apos;s running it&apos;s autoconf tests to make sure the ZFS headers are selecting the kernel-space codepaths.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am currently testing a patch that allows Lustre to build against zfs-2.4.0.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
